Great bargain, all 4 movies are very good, especially the one in England. Funny thing with the Tornado movie is elsewhere on Amazon as a single release it's OOP and going for a very High price. If you do a search for it this version does not come up. Anyway I highly recommend this set, each disc has 2 movies and they are both one sided disc.

Good movies and actors.  not hokie.

These made for television movies have provided me with enjoyable entertainment. Some of the movies have very well known actors, but others do not. The stories are interesting, and that is what matters to me. The price that I paid for the package of movies was very reasonable. I would recommend this package to others seeking the same type of entertainment.
Movies I have been looking  for. I'm so happy to have them now. 5 stars

I love disaster movies.  They are one of my Guilty Pleasures.  This is a good set of movies that are a little more realistic than the most and still have some of the thrills. It focuses on a story and disaster rather than some killer fixated on one of the people of the movie that just escaped prison that has nothing to do with the story.  These are good quality what i would expect from TV Guide.
